## Project layout

{% if project_type == 'library' -%}
Flat library layout. Public API at the root, internal packages under `internal/`.
{% elif project_type == 'study-tutorial' -%}
Cenário-named packages, each runnable and testable independently:

```
{% if study_entrypoint == 'cli' -%}
cmd/concurrency/         dispatcher (--pattern <name>)
{%- else -%}
cmd/api/                 dispatcher (POST /run/<name>)
{%- endif %}
internal/
{% for name in domain_names.split(',') -%}
  {{ name | trim }}/             Run(ctx, Params) (Result, error)
{% endfor -%}
{% if include_store -%}
  store/                 map+sync.RWMutex shared store
{%- endif %}
docs/
  foundations.md         text-only mental models
  decision-guide.md      when to reach for which primitive
```

Tests are race-aware (`-race`) and use `goleak` to assert no leaked goroutines.
{% elif project_type == 'multi-service-workspace' -%}
```
services/
{% for svc in service_names.split(',') -%}
  {{ svc | trim }}/
{% endfor -%}
```
{%- else -%}
```
cmd/{{ project_name }}/    entry point
internal/                  application logic
pkg/                       shared / exported helpers
```
{%- endif %}

